## 💻 Sample Code

### Password Hashing

```python
import bcrypt

password = "mypassword".encode()
hashed = bcrypt.hashpw(password, bcrypt.gensalt())
```

### Password Verification

```python
bcrypt.checkpw(password, hashed)
```

